text: Michelle Uhrig (born 20 January 1996) is a German speed skater. She competed in the women's 1000 metres at the 2018 Winter Olympics. In November 2019, she became the German national champion 1000 meter and 1500 meter. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:German female speed skaters Category:Olympic speed skaters of Germany Category:Speed skaters at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Competitors at the 2012 Winter Youth Olympics
